description:
Devi Lynn, aka “Spartica,” has never wrestled in a single season match up. She has one Tag Team match under her belt and 3 tournament matches. She was 2-1 in the Tournament and it can be said she is one of US’s elite wrestlers. She is tough and tenacious, and she has skills and some added college wrestling experience.

Madison Young, aka “The Butcher,” comes with some experience too. Both her father and brother were great wrestlers. Only time will tell if she can make the adjustment that so many others have struggled with.
title: Spartica(0-0) Not Ranked The Butcher(0-0) Not Ranked
